(Corrects acquisition figure in second paragraph.)    BBA Aviation Plc ’s net income last
year rose to 65.1 million pounds from 47.9 million pounds as
sales increased 9 percent to 1.18 billion pounds and pretax
profit jumped 42 percent to 85.2 million pounds.  The company said separately that its Ontic unit is buying a
legacy fuel-measurement business from  General Electric Co .’s
aviation division for $62.5 million.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
